 <span data-ttu-id="76db6-123">在下面的示例中，名为的数组中的字节 12-28 的值`arr`会复制到字节 0-16。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="76db6-123">In the following example, the values of bytes 12-28 in an array named `arr` are copied to bytes 0-16.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="76db6-124">同样，尽管有重叠的范围，还是已成功复制的源字节的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="76db6-124">Again, despite the overlapping range, the values of the source bytes are successfully copied.</span></span>  
  
